OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy with some showery rain this
OL,7,Fevening, although showers should ease
OL,8,Fovernight to leave mostly dry
OL,9,Fconditions, with some clear spells
OL,10,Fdeveloping. Turning locally chilly,
OL,11,Fwith light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA band of showery rain will
OL,14,Fmove slowly southeast during Friday
OL,15,Fafternoon, with some showers perhaps
OL,16,Fbecoming locally heavy. Generally
OL,17,Flight winds, with temperatures near
OL,18,Fnormal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
