OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA band
OL,6,Fof rain continues to move south on
OL,7,FSaturday. Breezy and cooler. Sunday,
OL,8,Fdry with sunny, winds easing. Monday,
OL,9,Fshowers moving south then brighter and
OL,10,Fcooler.
